node.text:
Wealth is what you DON’T see (the brokerage account, the real estate portfolio, the money that is making MORE money) 

not the fancy cars and designer clothes..

This page is from the book “the psychology of money” by Morgan Housel. One of the best personal finance books out there! 💯

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by The Market Hustle 👨‍💻 in New York, New York with @doughertytaxsolutions. May be an image of one or more people and text that says 'Grant Dougherty @doutaxsolutions How many of y'all would get an "IRS" tattoo tattooftmeowng if it meant never owing tax again?'.

node.text:
Who would do it? 😂

If you’re looking to learn more about the tax code, make sure to give me friend @doughertytaxsolutions a follow! No, IRS tattoos are not tax deductible 😂
It also makes it easier to buy assets that make you more money. Keep life simple, the luxuries can wait. 💯
New month, new challenge. Who’s in?
Master your emotions, and you’ll master money. 💯

Hope to see you all in the community! 💯

To join: go to my profile, select the “free discord” story post on my profile, & follow the instructions to join!

That's the power of starting early!'.

node.text:
The earlier you start investing, the longer your money will be able to work in your favor! Get started investing as soon as you start earning your first penny! 💯

#themarkethustle #stocks #money #invest #assets #cash #stockmarket

Money impacts all of us whether we like it or not. That’s the truth. That’s why it’s important to get your money game situated as soon as possible so you don’t have to stress out about money for your entire life. 

Get money, spend wisely, buy assets, and live a less stressful life. 💯🔥

#themarkethustle #money #stocks #invest #assets
